UPDATE bot_commands SET example = CASE command
  WHEN '!sync-team-roles' THEN '!sync-team-roles'
  WHEN '!sync-team-channels' THEN '!sync-team-channels'
  WHEN '!ab-records' THEN '!ab-records'
  WHEN '!badge' THEN '!badge Curry'
  WHEN '!update bid' THEN '!update bid Curry 50'
  WHEN '!regenerate-summary' THEN '!regenerate-summary'
  WHEN '/updatecap' THEN '/updatecap @Lakers 85'
  WHEN '!updateovercap' THEN '!updateovercap @Lakers 5'
  WHEN '!help' THEN '!help'
  WHEN '!ab-reset' THEN '!ab-reset'
  ELSE NULL
END
WHERE command IN ('!sync-team-roles', '!sync-team-channels', '!ab-records', '!badge', '!update bid', '!regenerate-summary', '/updatecap', '!updateovercap', '!help', '!ab-reset')
